{"tid":2314471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"針對香港  英國航母戰鬥群將長期部署日本","createTime":"2020-12-06T14:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T02:11:03.000Z","uid":227801,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2314d295870edf3fc2a01ebbbc8f051e3a8e051f","tid":2314471,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=415544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415544&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2u2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=d8ecb6b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415544&h=913e9e30\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=415544</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQ7MFrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQ7MFrv.jpg&h=0148ee33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJHHYdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJHHYdf.jpg&h=1ce7a1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】日本傳媒報道，英國航空母艦伊利沙伯女王號，將長期部署在西太平洋，駐日美軍將提供支援，以抗衡中國的海洋活動及威脅。<br />\n<br />\n日本共同社引述日本政府多名消息人士報道，英國海軍最快在明年初，長期將最尖端的航空母艦，伊利沙伯女王號及其戰鬥群，部署在包括沖繩縣等西南諸島周邊在內的西太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，伊利沙伯女王號會聯同日本自衛隊及美軍，舉行聯合演習。<br />\n<br />\n伊利沙伯女王號搭載F-35B隱形戰機，而三菱重工在愛知縣的工廠是亞太地區的F-35維修基地。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述相關人士指，當局正研究三菱重工的工廠，能否為航母上的戰機提供維修保養。<br />\n<br />\n而根據聯合國決議《聯合國軍地位協定》，英軍能在橫須賀和佐世保等駐日美軍設施及區域接受補給。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，日本政府有意深化與英國海軍的合作，展現對抗中國日益增加的海洋活動，並維護秩序的姿態，又說日本在西太平洋與有同盟關係的美軍，以及非周邊國的航母有持續軍事活動，極為罕見。<br />\n<br />\n背後的原因相信在於針對中國對南海的主權主張，以及英國政府對香港問題的強烈關切。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒早前亦曾報道，英軍計劃在明年初，把伊利沙伯女王號部署在印太地區，結合日本和美國，抗衡中國日益增加的威脅。"},{"pid":"b4174427aa986cd348dd40edc45bb5ba0929b7ba","tid":2314471,"uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"黎明來到"},{"pid":"51d978c74bfde7938ec25de4e380761eb66699e8","tid":2314471,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"英日同盟"},{"pid":"6a6e49ae0aca96efaa862a7b49ce4f90917f445f","tid":2314471,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"除咗QE之外,英國仲有隻PW未出, 遲吓可以玩吓雙航母"},{"pid":"b245c35449e4b8d10cacc73c081ffd6d1cfa5823","tid":2314471,"uid":257622,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:42:23.000Z","msg":"準備再簽南京條約"},{"pid":"951af0e07eb87fa23e8e0d65f7436818d723d5ac","tid":2314471,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a6e49ae0aca96efaa862a7b49ce4f90917f445f","tid":2314471,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"除咗QE之外,英國仲有隻PW未出, 遲吓可以玩吓雙航母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"如果英國都要雙航母, 我諗美國嚟五六隻都似"},{"pid":"491099d8c63a3bb92636e1f8ed14df5622281d40","tid":2314471,"uid":355289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"英 美 澳 日 印打到門口中共都仲係道加速緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f795a1c00521c46cd3622e168b9060f8f43a2816","tid":2314471,"uid":197640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51d978c74bfde7938ec25de4e380761eb66699e8","tid":2314471,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"英日同盟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:26:18.000Z","msg":"一百年之後再黎一次英日同盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f6db97d7017f02d863ba7717627f441d865406","tid":2314471,"uid":384590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"可能真係歸英"},{"pid":"903db8a19b1347f0fb97039f3048a06749df